#Sometimes it is necessary to notice unacceptable letter combinations
#on the fly
#The following are letter sequences that might be produced in OCR
# but which are not acceptable in Komi orthography
#
##Letters that cannot follow the soft sign
ь(ъ|э|а|і)
##Letters that cannot follow the hard sign
ъ(ъ|а|о|у|ы)
##Letters that cannot preceed the Imperial "і"
(а|я|о|ё|э|е|у|ю|і|и|ы|б|в|г|ж|й|к|м|п|р|ф|ч|и|щ|х|ш)і
